Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.72,0:01:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.26,0:01:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是我和师傅以前一起修练的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.51,0:01:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.42,0:01:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错，而我现在要在这里把变成\NSUPER MODE运用自如！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，各位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.34,0:01:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在南美基亚拿高地这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.29,0:01:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙·卡休正在拼命修练
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.90,0:02:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给神秘蒙面战士舒柏兹·布鲁达
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.66,0:02:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指出自己还未成熟的多蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次回到他以前跟师傅一起修练的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.50,0:02:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了把SHINING GUNDAM SUPER MODE运用自如
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后打倒Devil Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他究竟会顺利达到目的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.49,0:02:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日的对手是宿命原竞敌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.72,0:02:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇波迪·库罗克特和他的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.69,0:02:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，他的状态有点古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么，GUNDAM FIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,READY GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.31,0:02:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}盗取必杀技！美女军团的大作战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.02,0:02:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旋风拳被…！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.13,0:03:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点本事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇波迪！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.46,0:03:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是…！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Gundam的细胞！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇波迪！住手！奇波迪！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了，对方不能动了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.55,0:04:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是…！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.53,0:04:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这全是我做的吗！？我…！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我究竟怎么了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.09,0:04:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇波迪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.58,0:04:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.38,0:04:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样子，neo America的梦想也完了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他简直好像怕了战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.91,0:04:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷失了自我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么！大叔！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.86,0:04:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时候只好忘记一切
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.38,0:04:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一心一意的认真战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，对手越强大越好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:05:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而如果能燃起斗志拼命战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.54,0:05:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也就能再次成为闪亮之星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟他作出那种比赛的对手也不是没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.47,0:05:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，需要一个强大的竞敌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思啊！那大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.06,0:05:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对事情根本一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.25,0:05:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他讲得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇波迪现在需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一场精彩的比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，他口中的那种对手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.59,0:05:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，那家伙叫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.95,0:05:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙·卡休！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.48,0:05:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.14,0:05:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.21,0:05:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼狮们最好便是互相锻练
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，我也要快点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，给我开门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然上了锁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉！拿杯水给我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.43,0:06:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芭妮，姬丝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.08,0:06:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍妮，都不在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.59,0:06:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是一封信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.79,0:06:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们竟然瞒著我多管闲事！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.73,0:06:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的奇波迪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们四人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.79,0:07:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能眼睁睁看着你意志消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.93,0:07:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，我们决定前去基亚拿高地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替你打倒多蒙·卡休
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.89,0:07:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们以Gundam Fighter成员的尊严发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再者，你有兴趣的便来观战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们究竟想干什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅…！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.48,0:08:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连这么矮的瀑布也克服不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎能战胜师傅…！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.84,0:08:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.55,0:08:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙只会跳进河里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样真的能锻练身手吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会留在这种地方太久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.50,0:08:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这里空气清新
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之很沉闷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.91,0:08:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她看来睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.07,0:08:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒…失…鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.54,0:08:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.81,0:08:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇波迪跟我们联络也别管他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.61,0:09:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我们不是真的要毁灭Shining Gundam吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.59,0:09:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今你说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是来复制Shining Gundam的战斗数据
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，那很差劲啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.66,0:09:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，我们要暂时变回以前的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前…你指的那时候吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.90,0:09:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们故乡也跟奇波迪一样是纽约的商业区
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们被称为一无是处的不良少女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.89,0:09:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们做过很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.77,0:09:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷窍、行骗，在市内四处捣乱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使明知是为非作歹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.24,0:09:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了生存也逼于无奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.55,0:09:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为大家的梦想都是前往憧憬的卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但毕竟不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得我们潜入穿梭机偷渡入境
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差点就成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果我们被发现，给捉住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:09:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.94,0:10:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在那里偶然遇上的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.79,0:10:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是奇波迪·库罗克特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.26,0:10:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼睛明亮照人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.04,0:10:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就像以前的我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？你们肯在我那里工作吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会刻薄你们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他是第一个重视我们的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，我们曾经发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论何时何地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.29,0:10:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也要尽全力帮他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.56,0:10:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要从Shining Gundam的数据里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出它的弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.17,0:10:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何要令奇波迪取胜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我睡着了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.06,0:10:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新宿一战仍然令我很疲倦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:11:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了，我还要去整理SUPER MODE的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.28,0:11:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.26,0:11:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要动，否则我会开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们究竟在这里做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看便知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.09,0:11:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说笑的，别妨碍我们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Fighter成员可以做这种事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指这种事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.39,0:11:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shining Gundam的数据我全部拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.51,0:11:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.54,0:11:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好！数据…！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.01,0:11:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们自以为是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们真的以为能打倒多蒙·卡休吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.15,0:11:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，这里挺壮观啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种景色在卫星是看不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那瀑布也非常高
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.34,0:12:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在那种地方！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.90,0:12:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙·卡休！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.41,0:12:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是那个日本人！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.82,0:12:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.83,0:12:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个日本人在这种地方做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.31,0:12:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…真是气势逼人！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他究竟做什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.48,0:13:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…他在跟Devil Gundam战斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，不会有错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不只跟我一样在苦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.16,0:13:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还展望将来努力苦练
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.21,0:13:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一心想想着跟它正面交锋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.41,0:13:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了，我也要克服我对Devil Gundam的恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.79,0:13:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以用我的Fighter灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙虎相斗，有趣起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人斗志令到风起云涌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.88,0:13:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得得到数据！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放弃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.28,0:13:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，竟然能追上我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.32,0:13:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也很了得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着，我们分头走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们逃到哪里了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要抢回战斗数据
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很顺利呢，走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.74,0:14:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可大叫，芭妮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.58,0:14:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我最讨厌蛇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把数据还给我！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.34,0:14:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样苦练也未能令这柄刀削铁如泥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.49,0:15:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以日本刀来说那柄刀造得粗糙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.83,0:15:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇波迪·库罗克特！？又是你吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想用那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟Devil Gundam交手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.11,0:15:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那和你无关
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.34,0:15:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那已经完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙·卡休，我要挑战你！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.51,0:15:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你来试试修练的成果也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.97,0:15:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我奉陪到底！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.22,0:15:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才像样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.09,0:15:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maxter！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.29,0:16:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM FIGHT！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,READY…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.94,0:16:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这招
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从跟他的战斗里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.85,0:16:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也领悟了新招式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.23,0:16:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇波迪的惊人气势
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不用再修练了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看，他们两人在比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.91,0:16:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇波迪果然追着我们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来没断骨，但暂时不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.16,0:16:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们干吗偷去高达的数据？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是为了奇波迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.62,0:16:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芭妮，姬丝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.36,0:16:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.44,0:16:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉，姬丝受了伤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.11,0:17:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没大碍，莉茵也已经给我包扎了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来抢回数据吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能打赢我们三人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.16,0:17:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说那些，我们要快点离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.29,0:17:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.32,0:17:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点…！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.11,0:17:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.03,0:17:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水位不断升高！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去很危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.37,0:17:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.83,0:17:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫奇波迪来救我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,0:17:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊，芭妮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？叫他来救我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.34,0:17:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，只是那件事做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.06,0:17:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们身为成员的尊严不容许
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.55,0:17:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，成员跟战士是一心同体的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.48,0:17:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要互相扶持才能称为同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要他营救也毫不羞耻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.32,0:18:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉，叫奇波迪来，我求你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.57,0:18:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了…我叫他来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…SOS讯号弹！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.47,0:18:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉她们吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.69,0:18:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么？奇波迪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.89,0:18:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.28,0:18:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇波迪！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这…！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点波涛，我要挡住它！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.13,0:18:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SHINING FINGER
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.16,0:19:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那能挡住它吗！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.80,0:19:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇波迪！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.47,0:19:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会保护莎莉她们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.13,0:19:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇波迪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.45,0:19:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候拥有这种力量！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢材！你在做什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面也有你的成员吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.47,0:19:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.68,0:19:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.70,0:19:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救我！多蒙！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.89,0:19:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.40,0:19:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SHINING FINGER
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.33,0:20:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是我的力量！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.76,0:20:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好，多蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的声音…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.62,0:20:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不需要我帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，真正的修练现在才开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.06,0:20:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己心想时，自己需要时
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟能否运用自如
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.88,0:20:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.16,0:20:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙，你的修练
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.36,0:20:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后也要让我好好欣赏才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.26,0:20:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SHUT UP
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.06,0:20:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得的数据…！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.37,0:20:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.13,0:21:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白我的心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.30,0:21:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，我们没资格当你的成员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.39,0:21:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家，走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.75,0:21:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪里？莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.32,0:21:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全靠你们，我才能练成新招式
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.44,0:21:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，要继承Queen of Spades的称号
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.81,0:21:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看来还未有资格
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.21,0:21:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我和你们要一起修练
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.15,0:21:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会重新锻练你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.46,0:21:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好心理准备啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.60,0:21:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇波迪…！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.93,0:21:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都有一双明亮的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.53,0:21:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以前一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:21:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.16,0:22:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们…也要努力修练呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.92,0:22:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是

Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.83,0:22:30.43,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便数千的日夜流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.78,0:22:34.82,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所到达的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.07,0:22:39.26,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨着 追求着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.73,0:22:42.83,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫步着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.08,0:22:49.98,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋人啊 在我瞳孔的深处
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.46,0:22:55.68,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实摇曳着的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.88,0:23:00.99,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要如何传达才好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.11,0:23:07.48,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让受伤的心与身体
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.88,0:23:11.65,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这温暖的怀抱中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.78,0:23:17.64,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比海更深沉的睡去吧

Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.86,0:23:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.96,0:23:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在多蒙不知疲倦地修行的基亚拿高地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.65,0:23:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔡斋西和阿鲁哥展开激烈战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.86,0:23:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是Death Army的魔手悄悄的伸到了他们身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.43,0:23:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动武斗传G GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.79,0:23:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激斗！Dragon Gundam对Bolt Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.74,0:23:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,READY GO！


